body_html: Most likely it is a big-endian vs little endian issue in snappy buffers. As usual, we don't really have a great way to debug this, but you should be able to look at the code and find raw buffer interpretations that need endian swaps included for the big-endian case.

body: Most likely it is a big-endian vs little endian issue in snappy buffers.  As usual, we don't really have a great way to debug this, but you should be able to look at the code and find raw buffer interpretations that need endian swaps included for the big-endian case.
